----------------------------------------
🔹 【mp_rewards_claim】
   说明: [Multiplayer Rewards] Claim a reward from the post-combat rewards screen.

Args:
    reward_index: 0-based index of the reward.

----------------------------------------
🔹 【mp_rewards_pick_card】
   说明: [Multiplayer Rewards] Select a card from the card reward screen.

